headline: MSIG USA Appoints David Petrone as Northeast Region Distribution Leader
summary: MSIG USA, a leading provider of specialty insurance solutions, announced today the appointment of David Petrone as Northeast region distribution leader. Petrone brings more than three decades of industry experience and will report to Joseph Fitzpatrick, head of distribution for MSIG USA.
